<refentry xml:id="function.decbin" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>decbin</refname>
  <refpurpose>10진수를 2진수로</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
   <methodsynopsis>
    <type>string</type><methodname>decbin</methodname>
    <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>number</parameter></methodparam>
   </methodsynopsis>
  <para>
   주어진 <parameter>number</parameter> 인수의 2진 표현을 가지는 문자열을
   반환합니다. 변환할 수 있는 가장 큰 수는 10진수 4294967295로, 결과는 32개의
   1을 가지는 문자열입니다.
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  <para>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>number</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       변환할 10진 값
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <para>
   <parameter>number</parameter>의 2진 문자열 표현
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="examples">
  &reftitle.examples;
  <para>
   <example>
    <title><function>decbin</function> 예제</title>
    <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
echo decbin(12) . "\n";
echo decbin(26);
?>
]]>
    </programlisting>
    &example.outputs;
    <screen>
<![CDATA[
1100
11010
]]>
    </screen>
   </example>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="seealso">
  &reftitle.seealso;
  <para>
   <simplelist>
    <member><function>bindec</function></member>
    <member><function>decoct</function></member>
    <member><function>dechex</function></member>
    <member><function>base_convert</function></member>
   </simplelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
</refentry>

